title: 588. 10 Takeaways from Week 2
itunes:title: 588. 10 Takeaways from Week 2
description:
Daniel Jeremiah, Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis look back at the weekend and pick ten storylines that stood out from Week 2 of the NFL season. To start off, the guys discuss how the Cowboys came back and won ugly against the Falcons (1:32). Later, the trio analyze the Packers explosive offense (19:18). After that, the guys look at Cam Newton and Russell Wilson's matchup, which lived up to the hype (22:35). To wrap up the show, DJ and Bucky explain why Josh Allen is clutch (33:37). All that and more in this packed episode.
